  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hey! This is XPS Contractor Assist \u2014 your AI operations engine for Xtreme Polishing Systems. I manage leads, write proposals, send emails & texts, make AI calls, research competitors, build business plans, and handle invoices. I execute immediately \u2014 just tell me what you need done."
